{
  "3265230": {
    "name": "Cursed Companions",
    "steam_appid": 3265230,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cursed Companions is a co-op horror game that responds to every word the players say. Every player is <strong>cursed with a forbidden word</strong>, like “<i>Okay</i>” or “<i>I think</i>”. If anyone says it, the player takes damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/ead89395d70bd6e45570a629b03ef5d3.poster.avif?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/ead89395d70bd6e45570a629b03ef5d3.webm?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/ead89395d70bd6e45570a629b03ef5d3.mp4?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/3269073ec55f5ebaeb6118520e903436.webp?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you say the <i><strong>right</strong></i> words, you can heal your friends or disarm traps. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/e4ff25926d108f4f3eacc01f230b014c.poster.avif?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/e4ff25926d108f4f3eacc01f230b014c.webm?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/e4ff25926d108f4f3eacc01f230b014c.mp4?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;Mommy loves you... I'm sorry, I'm sorry... IT'S IN THE BOOK! IT'S IN THE BOOK!&quot; - MichiMochievee</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But when you say the <i><strong>wrong</strong></i> words (i.e. &quot;Follow me!&quot;) you could wipe out your team. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/a4043ac3dfcc10f267ccaedfffbfa34d.poster.avif?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/a4043ac3dfcc10f267ccaedfffbfa34d.webm?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/a4043ac3dfcc10f267ccaedfffbfa34d.mp4?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/cb75afd240449a368b385c94d8e3b295.webp?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeons are <strong>randomly generated</strong>, every run is a brand-new experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/4325386c7195264795fb0b11e73946de.poster.avif?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/4325386c7195264795fb0b11e73946de.webm?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/4325386c7195264795fb0b11e73946de.mp4?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/8289933ed974e331b1b37db3a1a8ad66.webp?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over twenty different monsters to encounter and ‘befriend’.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/b9f25dd3198b58b7d770f8f986ae8291.poster.avif?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/b9f25dd3198b58b7d770f8f986ae8291.webm?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/b9f25dd3198b58b7d770f8f986ae8291.mp4?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Foul Moth</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/9640e1e97e44878d5f1ea1e1721272f6.poster.avif?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/9640e1e97e44878d5f1ea1e1721272f6.webm?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/9640e1e97e44878d5f1ea1e1721272f6.mp4?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;[The Foul Moth] kinda looks like a Labubu.&quot; - QuarterJade. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Watch your mouth! </strong>The <strong>Foul Moth</strong> punishes players who swear. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Meatgrinder</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/a58ddef2cddb9653d31a2b165546c793.poster.avif?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/a58ddef2cddb9653d31a2b165546c793.webm?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/a58ddef2cddb9653d31a2b165546c793.mp4?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roast or get roasted! </strong>Shout <strong>“</strong>Who’s your daddy!” to send the <strong>Meatgrinder</strong> packing!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Bride</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/b2b82b8e45b024244fea452047f778d2.poster.avif?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/b2b82b8e45b024244fea452047f778d2.webm?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/b2b82b8e45b024244fea452047f778d2.mp4?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scare The Bride away</strong>! Bad pickup lines and awkward confessions are your best defense! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/d6c9eb6152db41de2e7cc6848a767bbf.webp?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up and tackle a variety of co-op modes. Battle bosses in two standalone stages or dive into tougher dungeons in <strong>Challenge Mode</strong>. Push your limits in <strong>Endless Mode</strong> to see how long you can survive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/a5c8b479331ecc0ceb04d1b70626e513.webp?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monsters aren’t the real threat in Traitor Mode; your so-called friends are. It’s a chaotic social deduction mode where Traitors secretly sabotage the mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/134005e1555b8b3974b6d29d8d50d8aa.poster.avif?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/134005e1555b8b3974b6d29d8d50d8aa.webm?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/134005e1555b8b3974b6d29d8d50d8aa.mp4?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>But don’t be too obvious as others can call an ‘Emergency Meeting’ to vote you out! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/c0b3aa23322dbcb2f19cd42209ba34f9.webp?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=63 /></span>Unlock unique skins as rewards for your greatest achievements! Kill bosses, survive brutal challenges, or simply get killed in unique circumstances. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/19bf5baca22e771b44f3c45c05aa3939.poster.avif?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/19bf5baca22e771b44f3c45c05aa3939.webm?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/19bf5baca22e771b44f3c45c05aa3939.mp4?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>“Oh that’s nice… I can be a knight!” - Foolish</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/a0cbf76b61fff084a30e9fb5d4d486d2.webp?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your home and let your friends see how cursed your taste really is! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/2d662b048701be40f2bcfa7fa59aaa97.poster.avif?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/2d662b048701be40f2bcfa7fa59aaa97.webm?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/2d662b048701be40f2bcfa7fa59aaa97.mp4?t=1766152963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/c34d7e776dc6319396f5639c08af108e.webp?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=63 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voice Control </strong><br>The game is 'always listening', the game uses voice-activation game mechanics. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Everyone gets a forbidden word </strong><br>Like “Okay” or “I think” or “Didn’t”. If anyone says it, you take damage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Say the right words to get ahead </strong><br>Use your voice to light your torch, to disable traps or shoo monsters away. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Say the wrong words to your peril </strong><br>Your voice can awaken monsters, hurt you and even your teammates. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedural Dungeons </strong><br>Every run is a brand new experience. The dungeons go deep, so try not to get lost!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Co-op or Traitor Mode </strong><br>Play as a team in Co-op Mode or find the Traitor in an ‘Among Us’-style Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Magical Items </strong><br>Buy equipment like the Teleport Stone, Ice Wand, Stink potions and more. Use the equipment in your own creative ways to try and survive the dungeons and fend off monsters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Monsters </strong><br>Voice-activated monsters, creatures that track by vision or sound and many more interesting monsters to meet.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Language Mod Support </strong><br>Currently only supports <u><strong>English</strong></u> with upcoming betas in German, French, Spanish and Chinese. Will provide easy instructions to add your own language using alternative language voice models.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265230/extras/c95249039b9be0a619f1857433e012e1.webp?t=1766152963\" width=800 height=63 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Early Access will arrive in Q4 2025</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More Abyssal Lands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different Dungeon environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team versus Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More scary monsters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More Items and Equipment</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More in our series of Roadmap articles in our Community posts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
